    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "みんながお使いに行ったタイミングで\n沢山お客さんが来てビックリしたね",
      "startTime": 9.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-cca002.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃんとすみれちゃんがいてくれたから\nなんとかなったよ～！　ありがとう！",
      "startTime": 15.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、私の方こそありがとう。ココアちゃんと\nチノちゃんが丁寧に教えてくれたおかげだよ",
      "startTime": 22.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-cca003.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、そうかなぁ。お姉ちゃんだと思って\nもっともっと頼ってくれていいからね？",
      "startTime": 30.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、ありがとう\nでも、お姉ちゃんはもういるから大丈夫、かな",
      "startTime": 36.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-cca004.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、千紗ちゃんってお姉ちゃんがいるんだ～\nどんな人？　千紗ちゃんみたいな癒し系だったりして！",
      "startTime": 44.420387554,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "ふぇ……！？　私って癒し系なのかな？\nえへへ、私のお姉ちゃんは、真面目な人って感じかな",
      "startTime": 53.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
